com.mavenproject.timescheduler.dialogs

Class ConsoleDialogBody

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mavenproject.timescheduler.dialogs.ConsoleDialogBody
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IConsoleDialogBody
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConsoleDialogBodyAskForValue, ConsoleDialogBodyChooseMenu, ConsoleDialogBodyInfo

    public class ConsoleDialogBody
extends Object
implements IConsoleDialogBody
    Trieda reprezentuje elementy, ktore budu vygenerovane a zobrazene v tele dialogu. Je implementaciou intefacu IConsoleDialogBody. Kazde subzobrazenie v dialogu je zlozene prave z intancii ConsoleDialogBody.

      • addConsoleDialogElements

        public void addConsoleDialogElements(List<ConsoleDialogElement> consoleDialogElements)
        Metoda prida pomedzi vygenerovane dilcie elementy dialogu este dalsie elementy. Typicky ak treba do predpripraveneho menu este pridat nejake elementy obsahujuce informacie navyse. Je to v situaciach, kedy je lepsie nemenit cele menu, ak chceme pridat nejaky riadok.
        Specified by:
        addConsoleDialogElements in interface IConsoleDialogBody
        Parameters:
        consoleDialogElements - Zoznam elementov, ktore sa dodatocne pridaju do menu/dialogu
